Guildleader: <a href=http://www.guildvision.org>Vision</a></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#383838><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub42.ezboard.com/usirtaino.showPublicProfile?language=EN>SirTainO</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Local Resident</span><br> <font color=#ff0000>(12/21/01 12:47:24 am)</font><br>     <br>Community Supporter<br> <BR><img src=http://www.jollyjokers.com/images/pally.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: They said give up your Epic.</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> why the hell does the leader deserve the epic the most?<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
